OL,3,CCharges brought over deaths of three
OL,4,CVespa riders in Wiltshire
OL,6,FA man has been charged with causing
OL,7,Fthe deaths of three Vespa riders by
OL,8,Fdangerous driving.
OL,10,FHugh Campion, 70, will appear before
OL,11,FSalisbury Magistrates' Court in August
OL,12,Fto face four offences.
OL,14,FThe charges relate to an incident on
OL,15,Fthe A36 at Knook in Wiltshire, at
OL,16,Fabout 10.30am on May 31 last year.
OL,18,FA Toyota Prius driven by Campion is
OL,19,Falleged to have collided with three
OL,20,FVespas travelling in the opposite
OL,21,Fdirection.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
