OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777057867
OL,3,CCharges brought over deaths of three
OL,4,CVespa riders in Wiltshire
OL,6,FRobert Best, 62, died at the scene,
OL,7,Fwhile Marie Jones, 64, and Timothy
OL,8,FDavies, 62, died in hospital.
OL,10,FA man in his 60s suffered serious
OL,11,Finjuries.
OL,13,FPolice constable Paul Brewster, of
OL,14,FWiltshire Police, said: "This is a
OL,15,Fsignificant development in our
OL,16,Finvestigation into this tragic
OL,17,Fcollision, in which three people lost
OL,18,Ftheir lives and a fourth suffered
OL,19,Fserious injuries.
OL,26,@vD@YOU
