CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777057867
OL,3,CCharges brought over deaths of three
OL,4,CVespa riders in Wiltshire
OL,6,F"Our thoughts continue to be with
OL,7,Ftheir friends and families and they
OL,8,Fcontinue to be supported by specially
OL,9,Ftrained officers.
OL,11,F"As the case will now proceed to
OL,12,Fcourt, I would ask the public not to
OL,13,Fspeculate on the collision so as to
OL,14,Fnot prejudice the proceedings."
OL,16,FCampion, of Upton Scudamore,
OL,17,FWiltshire, has been issued a summons
OL,18,Fto appear before Salisbury
OL,19,FMagistrates' Court on August 14.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@_O]
